John D'Errico
http://www.mathworks.com/matlabcentral/fileexchange/9428

"Re: moving standard deviation for time series"
Roger Stafford
http://newsgroups.derkeiler.com/Archive/Comp/comp.soft-sys.matlab/2006-05/msg00833.html

code snippet to convert amplitude to dB
http://hans.fugal.net/blog/2009/04/02/dft-magnitudepower-spectra (accessed 2009, no longer available)
and Spectrogram by Sean Fulop, as a "modification and extension to Paul Kienzle's spectrogram program for Octave"
https://au.mathworks.com/matlabcentral/fileexchange/1553-spectrogram--short-time-ft-log-magnitude- (2018)

